{"tid":2278430,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"學生和你Shop被捕後頭破血流 拘捕警員否認打頭 稱不知傷勢何來","createTime":"2020-11-09T07:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T08:43:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2aabe54e240b0de9c5e23402cb48a9700287bb1c","tid":2278430,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:04:02.000Z","msg":"網民去年平安夜發起「和你Shop」活動，有學生當晚被指在尖沙嘴海港城內拒捕，因而被拘控，案件今續審。拘捕被告的便衣警供稱自己曾用伸縮棍擊打被告小腿，但否認曾擊打他的頭部。至於便衣警事後發現被告右邊眼眉有半吋長裂傷、左耳後有一吋長裂傷，並且左臉紅腫，他則稱不能肯定被告傷勢從何而來。<br />\n<br />\n負責拘捕首被告的便衣警10356曾耀華供稱，當日接報到海港城2樓中庭增援，發現警長A從後騎在首被告背上，未幾雙雙仰後倒地。曾耀華上前協助制服，看見首被告不斷用手肘撞擊A的腹部，於是用伸縮警棍擊打被告小腿四下，及後雙手捉住被告右手鎖上手銬，然後再捉左手，將被告雙手鎖在背後。<br />\n<br />\n曾又稱，當日為首被告檢查傷勢，發現被告右邊眼眉有半吋長的裂傷，左耳後有一吋長裂傷，左臉紅腫。惟他聲稱不能肯定被告傷勢從何而來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/XCVHLAC3ZBBH3O2GKUMD5K5UCE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FXCVHLAC3ZBBH3O2GKUMD5K5UCE%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=5e442c4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201109%2FXCVHLAC3ZBBH3O2GKUMD5K5UCE%2F&h=e34492fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201109/XCVHLAC3ZBBH3O2GKUMD5K5UCE/</a>"},{"pid":"3b4d2dfd5d7320709b80740bce6f870097ff05a5","tid":2278430,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f19a3466d91cfe6223f051af0297b948a059ed","tid":2278430,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"